    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": ".\nSwelling, tenderness, and erythema of eyelids and superficial tissues surrounding the orbit\n+/-\nfever\nLack of\n:\nProptosis\nChemosis\nGlobe displacement\nLimitation of eye movements\nPain with eye movement\nDouble vision\nVision loss\n(indicates orbital apex involvement)",
